      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PACKHAM PUNCH (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (25.35) at Grafton in a Grade 5 over 450m. Rates highly and will give a great sight. MISS POLLYWOOD (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Grafton over 350m behind Star (20.36) in a Grade 5. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Can figure in the finish. REMI NATH (6) missed the frame last time when fifth (24.10) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Must be included in calculations. KINGSBRAE NOLA (8) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
